{"tid":2214310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小圈子採訪代記招　被轟審查傳媒","createTime":"2020-09-23T07:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:20:59.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76fd96d12273cb378423bf52236e1fd23404ba8a","tid":2214310,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"學校課程檢討專責小組昨向教育局提交報告，提出多項有關通識科的富爭議性建議，惟教育局一改以往安排記者會解釋專責小組報告慣例，僅以新聞稿形式交代和上載報告至教育局網頁，未有召開記者會。<br />\n<br />\n僅《大公》《文匯》等四紙媒有份<br />\n本報獲悉，教育局破天荒只安排《大公報》、《文匯報》、《星島日報》和《明報》作小圈子採訪，由主席陳黃麗娟「導讀」。有議員炮轟教局審查傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有電子傳媒曾向教育局查詢可否參與上述小圈子採訪，對方回應只有「少量被揀選的報紙」才能參與，又聲稱只是主席陳黃麗娟向記者「導讀」報告。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/DJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR09TLdcSQpL2-w-HQ-_q1dCT9sD-pHIyiMJF2ykqVWtvAq2Vp5-8fGXano\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FDJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR09TLdcSQpL2-w-HQ-_q1dCT9sD-pHIyiMJF2ykqVWtvAq2Vp5-8fGXano&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=1d03a15e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FDJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR09TLdcSQpL2-w-HQ-_q1dCT9sD-pHIyiMJF2ykqVWtvAq2Vp5-8fGXano&h=e3cfabab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/DJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR09TLdcSQpL2-w-HQ-_q1dCT9sD-pHIyiMJF2ykqVWtvAq2Vp5-8fGXano</a>"},{"pid":"c0bb8630d753a35a1b814719e72679257dd6b374","tid":2214310,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"544f080d94bcfe7f9dfa9a4998d6792d2df404d8","tid":2214310,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，<del>好大機會</del><span class=\"gold\"><ins><strong>包括</strong></ins></span><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=e0c51bb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1b8c327f83aa54baa45eda052c3a2a7709320384","tid":2214310,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46dff75eea6b27f29114dec4186e66d17445edd3","tid":2214310,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"港產官媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}